  <hr>

  <p>Like I said before, these are the sources I've used over the last few years to find the books that have had the biggest influence on my life. I hope you find something that makes you think and helps you continue to grow.<p>

  <p><em>I'll continue to refine this list as I find more/better sources to discover great books.</em></p>
